newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle not well established - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle not well established - USDA.

text.p: Live Sales, compared with Thursday's close, slaughter steers and heifers not well established, USDA said. Trade slow. Demand and seller interest light. Offerings light and current. Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1250 lbs ld 71.00 Heifers - mostly Choice 2-4 1175-1200 lbs 2 ld 71.50.
Carcass Basis (weight only) Compared Thursdays close - Slaughter steers and heifers not well established.

Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1250 lbs 2 ld 116.00 Holstein - (weight only) Select to mostly Choice 2-3 1250-1400 lbs no sales Holsteins - ( grade and weight) Choice 2-3 1250-1450 lbs ld 106.00 Select 2-3 1250-1450 lbs 101.00.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales. Confirmed - 300 Week Ago - 4,400 Year Ago - 1,400
